# Supabase CLI local state - ephemeral CLI cache (which project this
# worktree is linked to, cached API versions), never meant to be
# committed. QRBooker (this repo's fork-sibling) had this checked in
# with the WRONG project ref, which pointed its CLI at this repo's own
# database. This repo's current ref happens to be correct, but the same
# gitignore gap existed here too - fixed as pre-flight for the
# QRWegn <-> WSMS milestone, before any --linked query runs against it.
supabase/.temp/
